    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#oliverio1927"/>, p. <citedRange>157</citedRange></bibl> (mention of find);
                    <bibl><ptr target="#oliverioTacc"/>, <citedRange>XI.6</citedRange></bibl>, whence
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SECir"/>, <citedRange>36</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>095400</citedRange></bibl>.
                    Cf. from <bibl><ptr target="#pernierTacc"/>, <citedRange>I.1925, p. 105</citedRange></bibl>,
                    <bibl><ptr target="#bartolini2014a"/>, p. <citedRange>167</citedRange>, fig. 9</bibl>.
                    </p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-64508"><name nymRef="#Κάλλιππος">Κάλλιππο<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied></name>
                    <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-62640"><name type="patronymic" nymRef="#Αἰγλάνωρ">Αἰγλάνορο<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied></name></persName></persName>
                    <lb n="3"/><w lemma="δεκάτα">δεκάταν</w>
                    <lb n="3a"/><space atLeast="1" unit="line"/>
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p>
                   <app loc="1">
                       <lem>Κάλλιππο<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied></lem>
                       <rdg resp="#SECir"><supplied reason="lost">Κ</supplied>άλλιππο<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied></rdg>
                   </app> 
                </p>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p>Kallippos fils d'Aiglanôr <supplied reason="subaudible">a consacré ce monument</supplied> comme dîme.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Kallippos son of Aiglanor <supplied reason="subaudible">dedicated this monument</supplied> as a tithe.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p>Kallippos figlio di Aiglanor <supplied reason="subaudible">ha dedicato questo monumento</supplied> come decima.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>The dedicant should be one of the <foreign rend="italic">thearoi</foreign> sent to Delphi mentioned at <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr064100</ref>.</p>
                <p>Pernier's archive kept at Macerata gives more information about the discovery (see <bibl><ptr target="#bartolini2014a"/>, p. <citedRange>167</citedRange>, fig. 9</bibl>).</p>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
